@startuml

title gitita Publish Sequence

actor Author

participant GitHub
participant "publish.yml" as CI
participant "gitita CLI" as Gitita
participant "Qiita API" as Qiita

Author -> GitHub : Merge PR to main

GitHub -> CI : Trigger workflow

CI -> Gitita : gitita publish

Gitita -> Gitita : Detect changed articles

Gitita -> Gitita : Parse markdown

Gitita -> Qiita : Upload image

Qiita --> Gitita : Image URL

Gitita -> Qiita : Create/Update article

Qiita --> Gitita : qiita_id

Gitita -> GitHub : Commit qiita_id

CI --> GitHub : Success / Failure

@enduml